<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>New Package Assignment - DropSecure</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #fff8f2; color: #333; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #800020 60%, #D4AF37 100%); color: #fff; padding: 24px 0; text-align: center; }
    .logo { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .content { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; margin: 32px auto; max-width: 480px; padding: 32px; box-shadow: 0 2px 12px #80002022; }
    .btn { background: linear-gradient(90deg, #D4AF37, #800020); color: #fff; padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block; margin-top: 24px; }
    .info-box { background: #fff8f2; border: 1px solid #D4AF37; color: #800020; border-radius: 8px; padding: 18px 24px; margin: 24px 0 0 0; font-size: 1.1em; }
    .footer { color: #800020; text-align: center; margin-top: 32px; font-size: 0.95em; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <span class="logo">DropSecure</span>
  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <h2 style="color:#800020;">New Package Assignment</h2>
    <p>Dear <%= courierName %>,</p>
    <p>You have been assigned a new package for delivery.</p>
    <div class="info-box">
      <h3>Package Details:</h3>
      <p><strong>Tracking Number:</strong> <%= trackingNumber %></p>
      <p><strong>Description:</strong> <%= packageDetails %></p>
      <h4>Pickup Information:</h4>
      <p><strong>Address:</strong> <%= pickupAddress %></p>
      <p><strong>Sender Phone:</strong> <%= senderPhone %></p>
      <h4>Delivery Information:</h4>
      <p><strong>Address:</strong> <%= deliveryAddress %></p>
      <p><strong>Receiver Phone:</strong> <%= receiverPhone %></p>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top:32px;">Please log into your courier dashboard to accept this assignment and update the package status.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="footer">
    &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> DropSecure. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</body>

</html></html>